t="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GHJDZZx.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/NmGWI71</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[sjac92303000]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Better late than never I guess</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/s9GqnsS</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/53Q8MrO.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://mobile.twitter.com/milestaylorusa/status/1526701781278986240</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/s9GqnsS</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[SpecialBrownies]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Baby sloth reunites with his mother.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/iaTOdJB</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ElbCGmW.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/iaTOdJB</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[VioletBunnyDraws]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Stuff i need off my phone, 3rd video edition</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Kq9uKBE</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/EiFM3dQ.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0KQdfKB.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4bJHPfr.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BXt98ud.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/lFyIOyg.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xjR6B5k.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BxNlmt8.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/is2CL7q.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zYINxra.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/V2AmnGb.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/km570A8.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Kq9uKBE</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[supergreenpasta]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>One upside to having ADHD is that you gain a new hobby/obsession every week! Here are some of mine:</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/XkZTx6m</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/c1kTG4X.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Post apocalyptic cosplay will always have a dirty place in my heart</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gRPErK4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I love to draw and I was blown away when an Imgurian recently reached out to buy a tattoo commission from me! My art is going to be on someone's body forever!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wd7rPB8.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>My last secret Santa where I made a viking style set of coasters and drinking horn holster. Leather work is probably my most rewarding passion.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fGrqZVX.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I try my best at baking but it is definitely a science. Here's a Portal cake replica I made for a birthday party.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Uc6WArZ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Probably my SO's favorite of my hobbies. Understandable since they get to eat the rejects AND the winners.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tl3nCZH.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Bartender by trade. Edible art is great when you can see the transition of happiness in people when they get to taste your concoctions.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VRs8jdt.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I love to grow plants and mushrooms alike! I had to fill my home with greenery since I live in the desert.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/sC69Rnh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Needle felting for when I feel like making cute tiny things. I made a replica of my axolotl</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kvyB0hy.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Camping is an essential break from the dread I start to feel when work and too many horrible news stories start to pile up. 5/7 would recommend.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tAr8yv4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This is Valley Of Fire State Park, NV. One of my top 3 favorite places to go.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UB0cQR4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Hammy the axolotl tax!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/XkZTx6m</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[LANAAAAAAAAAA]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Freedom from religion</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/PFpOjSp</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/znr8xvX.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/PFpOjSp</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Maitrify]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>THAT'S WHAT PRO-CHOICE IS YOU MORONIC DONUT